    NumberSerializers

    public static class NumberSerializers.DoubleSerializer
extends NumberSerializers.Base<java.lang.Object>
    This is the special serializer for regular Doubles (and primitive doubles)

    Since this is one of "native" types, no type information is ever included on serialization (unlike for most scalar types other than long).
